=</code></li> <li><code>\u5de6</code> <code>Ran#</code> <code>Ran#</code> <code>\u5de6</code> <code>\u5de6</code> <code>DEL</code> <code>\u4e0b</code>   (\u4e5f\u5c31\u662f\u4e0b\u9762\u7684 \u7ebf\u6027 SIGMA \u6ea2\u51fa )</li> <li><code>SHIFT</code> <code>8</code> <code>\u4e0b</code> <code>2</code> <code>6</code> <code>\u5de6</code> <code>\u5de6</code> <code>\u53f3</code></li> <li><code>9</code> <code>DEL</code> <code>\u5de6</code> \u5c4f\u5e55\u51fa\u73b0\uff1a</li> </ul> \\[ x=\\sum (x, 1, 1an\\] <p>\u7136\u540e\u5b8c\u5584\u8fd9\u4e2a\u5f0f\u5b50\u6210\uff1a</p> \\[ x = \\sum (x, 1, 1) + x \u4e2a\u6570\u5b57 + y \u4e2a\u6570\u5b57 an \\] <p>\u6309\u4e0b <code>CALC</code> <code>=</code> \u5373\u53ef</p>"},{"location":"docs/fx-991cnx/cnx/#GeZhong-YiChu","title":"\u5404\u79cd\u6ea2\u51fa","text":"<p>\u53c2\u8003\u6587\u6863 1 \u53c2\u8003\u6587\u6863 2 \u53c2\u8003\u6587\u6863 3 \u53c2\u8003\u6587\u6863 4</p>"},{"location":"docs/fx-991cnx/cnx/#YaLi-BUG-ZiFu-ZhuanHuanQi-LBF-ZhuanHuanQi-","title":"\u538b\u529b BUG\uff08\u5b57\u7b26\u8f6c\u6362\u5668 / LBF \u8f6c\u6362\u5668\uff09","text":"<ul> <li><code>SHIFT</code> <code>9</code> <code>3</code> <code>=</code> <code>AC</code> \u590d\u4f4d\u8ba1\u7b97\u5668\uff08\u53ef\u9009\uff09</li> <li><code>1</code> <code>SHIFT</code> <code>8</code> <code>\u4e0b</code> <code>2</code> <code>7</code> <code>=</code></li> <li><code>\u4e0a</code> <code>\u5de6</code></li> </ul>"},{"location":"docs/fx-991cnx/cnx/#ShuaKuang","title":"\u5237\u6846","text":"<ul> <li><code>SHIFT</code> <code>9</code> <code>3</code> <code>=</code> <code>AC</code> \u590d\u4f4d\u8ba1\u7b97\u5668\uff08\u53ef\u9009\uff09</li> </ul> <p>\u5728\u8ba1\u7b97\u5668\u5185\u8f93\u5165\uff1a</p> \\[ 6{\\div} 2((2+1\\sqrt{\\sqrt{\\sqrt{\\sqrt{\\sqrt{\\sqrt{\\sqrt{\\sqrt{\\sqrt{\\sqrt{\\sqrt{\\sqrt{1} } } } } } } } } } } }: \\sqrt{\\Box} \\] <ul> <li><code>6</code> <code>\u00f7</code> <code>2</code> <code>(</code> <code>(</code> <code>2</code> <code>+</code> <code>1</cod